msgctxt "668"
msgid "Sleepy Homeless Man"
msgstr "Vagabundo dormido"

msgctxt "100_Saejima"
msgid "Sorry to disturb your beauty sleep. You happen to see\\r\n"\n"a kid pickpocket come this way?"
msgstr "Lamento interrumpir tu sueño reponedor. ¿Has visto a un niño\\r\n"\n"ladrón pasar por aquí?"

msgctxt "112_Sleepy Homeless Man"
msgid "A young thief? You must mean Tadashi. As for where he is,\\r\n"\n"I don't know. Probably scrounging for coins off the floor."
msgstr "¿Un niño ladrón? Creo que es Tadashi. ¿Y dónde está?,\\r\n"\n"No lo sé. Probablemente recogiendo monedas del piso."

